      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Yes, it&#39;s safe to use existing api as my case, the library already in the project: to throw exception if invalid: Ints.checkedCast(long) and Ints.saturatedCast(long) to get the nearest for converting long to int."
